org.codice.ddf.catalog.plugin.metacard.backup.storage.filestorage

Class MetacardFileStorageRoute

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.camel.builder.BuilderSupport

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.camel.RoutesBuilder

    public class MetacardFileStorageRoute
extends MetacardStorageRoute
    Creates a camel route for storing metacards from post-ingest on the local file system. This route will transform the metacard using the configured metacard transformer prior to storage.
